##Nav##
h-left
j-down
k-up
l-right
d-delete
a-[mode->Edit]
n-branch
o-rival

##Edit##
esc-[mode->Nav]
focus->handle_key

C-w delete previous word
C-u clear text
/ search
n next search result
N previous search result

hash of command's stored as CH => COMMAND

##Delete Prev Word##
from current index, chomp chars backwards until reaching a punctuation character or a space
if multiple punctuation are in a sequence between a space they should all be cleared in one keystroke.
delete backwards until a change in punctuation or word

